@startuml state-population-matrix

' Note: COMPADRE matrices are always seeded as Public and never enter the deletion path.

skinparam defaultFontName Liberation Sans
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor white

skinparam state {
  BorderColor #003087
  BackgroundColor #EEF3FA
  FontColor #003087
  ArrowColor #333333
  ArrowFontColor #555555
  ArrowFontSize 10
}

[*] --> Draft : owner fills Create Matrix form

Draft : entry / validate matrix_a dimensions\ndo / allow owner to edit values

Draft --> Private : submit [matrix_a is square and non-empty]\n/ persist record (source_type = "custom")

Private : do / visible only to owner

Private --> Shared : share [target user exists]\n/ add user to shared_with list

Private --> Public  : make public\n/ set visibility = "public"

Private --> [*] : owner deletes\n/ DELETE /v1/matrices/{id}

Shared : do / visible to owner and shared users

Shared --> Private : revoke sharing\n/ clear shared_with entry

Shared --> [*] : owner deletes\n/ DELETE /v1/matrices/{id}

Public : do / visible to all visitors

Public --> Private : restrict access\n/ set visibility = "private"

Public --> [*] : owner deletes\n/ DELETE /v1/matrices/{id}

@enduml
